{"tid":1684442,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［黃色經濟圈］一人幾間被忽視嘅黃店","createTime":"2019-10-31T05:49:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T18:50:04.000Z","uid":33586,"like":26,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"dc2873d1b5f9c62f1ea3c406282f0b118c77d86e","tid":1684442,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T05:49:26.000Z","msg":"為咗唔好淨係幫襯出名嘅黃店<br />\n大家可以係到推介下 少人排隊嘅黃店 <br />\n等大家可以分散投資<br />\n<br />\n為防有偽黃同打手 <br />\n大家可以一次過推薦幾間同講下點黃法 <br />\n順便大家可以標明埋邊一區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先～深水埗區<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>Hana soft cream</strong></span><br />\n位於西九灣中心<br />\n黃店地圖有標示 不過去過幾次都見無乜人買<br />\n<br />\n老闆黃到金 <br />\n睇fb就知差唔多次次遊行時間都唔會營業<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/hanasoftcream/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fhanasoftcream%2F&d=N2LCmr%2FexNvWBpgyITFnAxZhTFX1FVJLw6RhI%2FCRHR8%3D&h=63ad5f11\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/hanasoftcream/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong>星河餐廳</strong></span><br />\n黃店地圖有標示 對比起周圍黃店嘅人流 唔算多<br />\n<br />\n門口有貼泛民候選人<br />\n老闆對黑衫人好好 好客氣<br />\n牛扒好好食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f2d434178bea8050c449ebf34e2c0647f17bdf9a","tid":1684442,"uid":13487,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T05:51:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/04EdLjM.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F04EdLjM.gif&h=e7e4e8ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"83c1a8bf6d2546962c104c1bc4cdb9b355b9df19","tid":1684442,"uid":33586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-31T05:55:53.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"cbf13a2e0073bc8b2abd0f7e11160abeeb4f0bf4","tid":1684442,"uid":4